ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Oriental Republic of Uruguay - Exchange of information on tax matters ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary, on behalf of Canada, to BRING INTO FORCE the AGREEMENT BETWEEN CANADA AND THE ORIENTAL REPUBLIC OF URUGUAY for the EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
